Instructions for the translations:

1. First get the .po file from the php files: xgettext -n *.php
2. Translate the messages.po file
3. Create the $LANG/LC_MESSAGES directory in locales/
4. Copy your translation to this newly created dir
5. Create the .mo file: with the command: cd locales/$LANG/LC_MESSAGES/ && msgfmt -c messages.po
6. Check functions.inc.php file: in getllang() function i created the $langs array to assign short lang and $LANG variable
